      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like strength. it just feels like i'm dragging myself through mud every day for no reason. everything is so empty. i'm just so tired of trying to find a reason to care when the only thing that mattered is gone. it feels like there's no way to stop the pain without just... stopping everything.",
